<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I can understand where you are coming from, but Robin McKinley was only 26 when this book was published. Also, I&apos;m not sure that the struggles/experie<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I can understand where you are coming from, but Robin McKinley was only 26 when this book was published. Also, I'm not sure that the struggles/experiences of teenagers change all that much, even if they are from different generations. That's just my opinion, but I would definitely say give it a chance :)<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
