<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1554693-am-i-the-only-one-who-read-this-book-and">Am I the only one who read this book and wondered if Disney mined it for ideas for their &quot;Beauty and the Beast&quot; adaptation? There are enough similarities between this book and the movie (Beauty loving books, the huge draft horse, the silverware and dishes and furniture moving by themselves) that it seems more than coincidence.</a>
</div>
