        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer78683178" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8981410746671033781">One of my favorite retellings of Beauty and the Beast. The family is loving and the prose beyond witty. If you love the Disney version, it owes a lot to this book. </span>

