        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3463782" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9854357554320740329">I can&apos;t believe I haven&apos;t reviewed this properly before! This book was so influential in the writing of my fairy tales! It has been so influential my writing in general! This book is the forerunner, and set the standard, for modern YA fairy tale retellings. And since the last time I read it I&apos;ve seen Disney&apos;s animated Beauty and the Beast roughly 9,000 times with my daughter, and I have to say: if they didn&apos;t pay McKinley for her ideas, Disney owes her big time! </span>
  <span id="freeText9854357554320740329" style="display:none">I can't believe I haven't reviewed this properly before! This book was so influential in the writing of my fairy tales! It has been so influential my writing in general! This book is the forerunner, and set the standard, for modern YA fairy tale retellings. And since the last time I read it I've seen Disney's animated Beauty and the Beast roughly 9,000 times with my daughter, and I have to say: if they didn't pay McKinley for her ideas, Disney owes her big time! </span>
